DESCRIPTION: Concatenated invoice and line number associated with the liquor order. This provides a unique identifier for the individual liquor products included in the store order.; e.g. S13371200019, S19585700010, S23228300021
Date of order; min: 2012-01-03, max: 2025-04-30
Unique number assigned to the store who ordered the liquor.; e.g. 2515, 6143, 5507
Name of store who ordered the liquor.; e.g. JOHNCY'S LIQUOR STORE, ROY'S FOODLAND, CASEY'S GENERAL STORE #3422 / NORWAL
Address of store who ordered the liquor.; e.g. 1101 ARMY POST RD. SUITE A & B, 1025 E 1ST ST, 915 SHORT ST #107
City where the store who ordered the liquor is located; e.g. POSTVILLE, WATERLOO, KNOXVILLE
Zip code where the store who ordered the liquor is located; e.g. 50677.0, 50201.0, 51534.0

Location of store who ordered the liquor. The Address, City, State and Zip Code are geocoded to provide geographic coordinates. Accuracy of geocoding is dependent on how well the address is interpreted and the completeness of the reference data used.; e.g. POINT(-93.238599958 43.14966099), POINT(-90.598528027 41.573777991)
Iowa county number for the county where store who ordered the liquor is located; e.g. 48, 52, 86
County where the store who ordered the liquor is located; e.g. SCOTT, FAYETTE, CASS
Category code associated with the liquor ordered; e.g. 1032100.0, 1051100, 1082200
Category of the liquor ordered.; e.g. AMERICAN VODKAS, IMPORTED DISTILLED SPIRITS SPECIALTY, CHERRY BRANDIES
The vendor number of the company for the brand of liquor ordered; e.g. 35, 85.0, 192.0
The vendor name of the company for the brand of liquor ordered; e.g. USDP / UNITED STATES DISTILLED PRODUCTS CO, PIEDMONT DISTILLERS INC, MOET HENNESSY USA, INC.
Item number for the individual liquor product ordered.; e.g. 67522, 101512, 101710
Description of the individual liquor product ordered.; e.g. CASAMIGOS BLANCO, PAUL MASSON GRANDE AMBER BRANDY VS, FIREBALL CINNAMON WHISKEY
The number of bottles in a case for the liquor ordered; min: 1, max: 336
Volume of each liquor bottle ordered in milliliters.; min: 0, max: 378000
The amount that Alcoholic Beverages Division paid for each bottle of liquor ordered; min: 0.0, max: 24989.02
The amount the store paid for each bottle of liquor ordered; min: 0.0, max: 37483.53
The number of bottles of liquor ordered by the store; min: -768, max: 15000
Total cost of liquor order (number of bottles multiplied by the state bottle retail); min: -9720.0, max: 279557.28
Total volume of liquor ordered in liters. (i.e. (Bottle Volume (ml) x Bottles Sold)/1,000)"; min: -1344.0, max: 15000.0
Total volume of liquor ordered in gallons. (i.e. (Bottle Volume (ml) x Bottles Sold)/3785.411784)"; min: -355.04, max: 3962.58
